{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"scriptGetSampleLanguage"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"script"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"PangoScript","preciseIdentifier":"c:@EA@PangoScript"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/Pango\/documentation\/Pango\/LanguageRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:5Pango11LanguageRefV","text":"LanguageRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The language will usually be the most widely spoken or used language"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"written in that script: for instance, the sample language for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cyrillic"},{"type":"text","text":" is ru (Russian), the sample language for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"arabic"},{"type":"text","text":" is ar."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For some scripts, no sample language will be returned because"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"there is no language that is sufficiently representative. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"best example of this is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"han"},{"type":"text","text":", where various different"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"variants of written Chinese, Japanese, and Korean all use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"significantly different sets of Han characters and forms"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of shared characters. No sample language can be provided"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for many historical scripts as well."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As of 1.18, this function checks the environment variables"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PANGO_LANGUAGE"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"LANGUAGE"},{"type":"text","text":" (checked in that order) first."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If one of them is set, it is parsed as a list of language tags"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"separated by colons or other separators. This function"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"will return the first language in the parsed list that Pango"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"believes may use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"script"},{"type":"text","text":" for writing. This last predicate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is tested using [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Pango.Language.includes_script"},{"type":"text","text":"]. This can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be used to control Pango’s font selection for non-primary"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"languages. For example, a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PANGO_LANGUAGE"},{"type":"text","text":" enviroment variable"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"set to “en:fa” makes Pango choose fonts suitable for Persian (fa)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instead of Arabic (ar) when a segment of Arabic text is found"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in an otherwise non-Arabic text. The same trick can be used to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"choose a default language for "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"han"},{"type":"text","text":" when setting"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"context language is not feasible."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pango\/scriptgetsamplelanguage(script:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Pango\/documentation\/Pango\/scriptGetSampleLanguage(script:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Finds a language tag that is reasonably representative of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"script"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"scriptGetSampleLanguage"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"script"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"PangoScript","preciseIdentifier":"c:@EA@PangoScript"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"LanguageRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:5Pango11LanguageRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"title":"scriptGetSampleLanguage(script:)","roleHeading":"Function","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"func","externalID":"s:5Pango23scriptGetSampleLanguage0B0AA0E3RefVSgSo0A6Scripta_tF","modules":[{"name":"Pango"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Pango\/documentation\/Pango"]]},"references":{"doc://Pango/documentation/Pango/LanguageRef":{"role":"symbol","title":"LanguageRef","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"LanguageRef"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PangoLanguage"},{"type":"text","text":" structure is used to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"represent a language."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Pango\/documentation\/Pango\/LanguageRef","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"LanguageRef"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pango\/languageref"},"doc://Pango/documentation/Pango":{"role":"collection","title":"Pango","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Pango\/documentation\/Pango","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pango"},"doc://Pango/documentation/Pango/scriptGetSampleLanguage(script:)":{"role":"symbol","title":"scriptGetSampleLanguage(script:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"scriptGetSampleLanguage"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"script"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"PangoScript","preciseIdentifier":"c:@EA@PangoScript"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"LanguageRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:5Pango11LanguageRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Finds a language tag that is reasonably representative of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"script"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Pango\/documentation\/Pango\/scriptGetSampleLanguage(script:)","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pango\/scriptgetsamplelanguage(script:)"}}}